   Strange as it may seem, the news of a potential uptick in
inflation proved to be good news for some of the high-tech stocks.
</P>
<P>
   Analysts say that with their prospects for high growth, certain
technology shares can fairly easily shrug off any moderate
increases in inflation.
</P>
