<HEADLINE> London shares Close higher  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   LONDON (AP) -- Gains in the technology sector pushed share prices
higher Friday on the London Stock Exchange.
</P>
<P>
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-Share Index of blue chip
stocks closed up 148.1 points, or 2.3 percent, at 6,327.4.
</P>
<P>
   Technology stocks rose following Thursday's strong performance
by New York's Nasdaq market and continued to rise after early
Nasdaq gains Friday.
</P>
<P>
   Provisional market volume was 1.3 billion shares, compared with
1.49 billion on Thursday.
</P>
</TEXT>
